review: I booked an online appointment for consult and i got attended on time. Dr first took the history very politely and examined my teeth. She explained the procedure to be done in detail so that i'm aware of what she's doing. Dr explained that the treatment will take 3-4 appointments to complete. She will have to do an uproot in one tooth and the adjacent tooth can be saved through a single sitting root canal therapy and then she will insert an bridge prosthetic. In the first appointment she did an uproot and i didn't feel any kind of pain or discomfort. She has given me the next appointment after 15 days. From the first experience the clinic was well equiped and hygeinic. Dr was very clear about the treatment  treatment plan and did it very calmly.
